                        <div id="collapseZero" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingZero" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p class="fst-italic">You can approach Castle Mountains from Walking Box Ranch Road off of Nevada State Rd 164 (Nipton Road) or from several unnamed dirt roads off of Lanfair Road in Mojave National Preserve.</p>
                            </div>
